commit message:
Ouch. The Schedule.Item.compareTo returned 0 for items that start at the
same time. TreeSet can't have two items that are equal so it was dropping
items. Try harder to find differences between items now.
Add 'My events' view, showing all items that have stars/reminders set.

For a 2-day schedule, when using the 'change day' option, just switch instead
of asking the user to tap the other day.
Show a 'nothing here' message in MyItemsView if there are 0 results.
